metadata.name: The World's Gone Mad, and I Just Want to Make Sense of It All
metadata.description:
The sun's gone missing, 
the city mutes its noise.

The streets fall frozen,  
and shadows fill the voids.

The diner is closed now, 
the last guest closed their tab.

Trying to make sense of it,  
but the world's gone mad.

-YAGAMIII
